@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam defaultFontName SansSerif
skinparam defaultFontSize 12

title ForkJoin Recursive Column Decomposition\n(Original image: 8192 columns, threshold = 50)

left to right direction

rectangle "Columns [0, 8192)\nHistogramTask" as root #FAFAFA {
  rectangle "Left [0, 4096)\nfork()" as L1 #F0F0F0 {
    rectangle "[0, 2048)\nfork()" as L2 {
      rectangle "[0, 1024)\nfork()" as L3 {
        rectangle "...\n≤ 50 cols\ncompute()" as L_LEAF
      }
      rectangle "[1024, 2048)\ncompute()" as L3_R {
        rectangle "...\n≤ 50 cols\ncompute()" as L_LEAF2
      }
    }
    rectangle "[2048, 4096)\ncompute()" as L2_R {
      rectangle "...\n≤ 50 cols\ncompute()" as L_LEAF3
    }
  }
  rectangle "Right [4096, 8192)\ncompute()" as R1 #F0F0F0 {
    rectangle "[4096, 6144)\nfork()" as R2 {
      rectangle "...\n≤ 50 cols" as R_LEAF1
    }
    rectangle "[6144, 8192)\ncompute()" as R2_R {
      rectangle "...\n≤ 50 cols" as R_LEAF2
    }
  }
}

note bottom of root
  ForkJoinPool.commonPool() — 11 worker threads.
  Work-stealing: idle threads pull tasks
  from busy threads' dequeues.
  
  ~164 tasks for 8192 cols / 50 threshold.
  Each leaf: 50 cols × 4608 rows = 230,400 pixels.
end note
@enduml
